# SEO Guidelines

## Page Metadata

Every page route should export metadata with at minimum:

```tsx
export const metadata: Metadata = {
  title: "Page Title",
  description: "Unique description under 160 characters.",
};
```

The root layout already sets `title.template: "%s — Khaled Ashraf"` so page titles auto-append your name.

## Blog Posts

Blog posts in `src/content/blog/*.mdx` should have complete frontmatter:

```mdx
---
title: "Descriptive Title"
date: "YYYY-MM-DD"
description: "Compelling description for search results and social sharing."
---
```

## URLs

- Keep URLs clean: `/projects/design-system` not `/projects/project-1`
- Use lowercase with hyphens, no underscores or special characters

## When Adding New Pages

1. Add unique title and description metadata
2. Update `public/sitemap.xml` with the new URL
3. If it's a blog post, the description becomes the search snippet

## OpenGraph Images (Future)

When ready to enhance social sharing, add `opengraph-image.png` files to route folders. Next.js auto-detects them.
